name: Diamond Animals Horse
description:
Diamond Animals Horse - 8th of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.

In a very fast gallop, in which the horse moves almost in leaps, it can reach speeds of up to 69.2 km / h. However, horses rarely gallop more than 2-3 kilometers, as they quickly tire at this pace. But this diamond horse can gallop for ages without getting tired.

----///----

1920 x 1920 px / 25 fps / Loop
